.</p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p>Dont get overconfident in your SUV vehicle. Many SUV are heavier than the passenger cars and take longer to stop. </p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p>Pay attention to the warning signs.</p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p>Don't stop on an icy hill if it's possible.</p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p>Keep your headlights on even in the daytime.</p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p>Select a vehicle that suits your needs. <strong>Volta4u </strong>has plenty of vehicle categories that cover all your needs, from Mini and SUVs to passenger and cargo Vans. Book your winter experience with us NOW. If you need any further information, please contact us via email at <strong>reservations@volta4u.com</strong> or via telephone at <strong>+30 2109735000</strong>.</p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"},{"__typename":"WpCoreParagraphBlock","originalContent":"<p></p>"}],"featuredImage":{"node":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='250'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20250'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%201l4%201c3%200%204%200%203%201L3%204%200%203v36c0%2035%200%2036%202%2036%201-1%202%200%203%201%202%203%209%2019%209%2022%201%203-6%2012-9%2012l-3-3-2-3v24h6l1%202%201%202c0%201-3%201-6-2-2-1-2%202-2%2059v61h66a975%20975%200%200092-1c-1%201%2012%201%2037%201l37-1c-1-1%200-2%201-2%202-1%200-4-3-6l-3-2c0-1-1-2-3-2-4%200-6-1-6-3l-1-2-2%201-1%201-1-1-1-1-3-1-4-2-2-3c-1-2-1-2-2-1h-1c0-2%200-2-2-2-1%201-1%20